and vitality of someone

00:36:25.230 --> 00:36:27.000 align:middle line:90%
who's five years older.

00:36:27.000 --> 00:36:28.800 align:middle line:90%
And he said, show me the data.

00:36:28.800 --> 00:36:31.170 align:middle line:84%
He'd been a physics
major in college.

00:36:31.170 --> 00:36:34.020 align:middle line:84%
